[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 3.15,
    "text": "- These kids back here have no idea what's about to happen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.15,
    "endTime": 5.699,
    "text": "I'm about to give them a hundred dollars in cash,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.7,
    "endTime": 7.15,
    "text": "one hour to spend it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.15,
    "endTime": 10.5,
    "text": "If they don't spend it in an hour they don't get anything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.5,
    "endTime": 11.3,
    "text": "Let's go surprise 'em."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.3,
    "endTime": 11.863000000000001,
    "text": "Come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.863,
    "endTime": 12.7,
    "text": "I have a challenge for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.7,
    "endTime": 13.84,
    "text": "You think you're up to it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.84,
    "endTime": 14.673,
    "text": "- Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.673,
    "endTime": 15.506,
    "text": "- What is that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.506,
    "endTime": 16.338,
    "text": "- Money."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.338,
    "endTime": 17.171,
    "text": "- A hundred dollars."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.219,
    "endTime": 18.851000000000003,
    "text": "(laughing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.851,
    "endTime": 19.851,
    "text": "- A hundred."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.61,
    "endTime": 23.311,
    "text": "(laughing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.973,
    "endTime": 24.805,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.806,
    "endTime": 28.200000000000003,
    "text": "- You have one hour to spend a hundred dollars."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.2,
    "endTime": 29.602,
    "text": "- I got an hour?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.81,
    "endTime": 32.5,
    "text": "- If you don't spend all the money in the hour"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.5,
    "endTime": 34.36,
    "text": "you don't get to keep anything you bought."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.36,
    "endTime": 35.595,
    "text": "What do you think you're going to do,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.595,
    "endTime": 36.449,
    "text": "what's your plan of attack?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.45,
    "endTime": 37.763000000000005,
    "text": "- Maybe give it to people?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.309,
    "endTime": 39.141,
    "text": "- Candy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.142,
    "endTime": 39.975,
    "text": "- Ice cream."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.975,
    "endTime": 41.1,
    "text": "- Let's go, let's find that ice cream."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.1,
    "endTime": 41.843,
    "text": "What are you going to get?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.843,
    "endTime": 43.86000000000001,
    "text": "- Stuff for my room and stuff for school."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.86,
    "endTime": 45.37,
    "text": "- [Host] Where do you wanna go, you have to make a decision."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.37,
    "endTime": 46.202,
    "text": "- Dylan's Candy Bar."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.203,
    "endTime": 47.53,
    "text": "- All right, you're going to Candy Bar first?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.53,
    "endTime": 49.86,
    "text": "Ready, the timer starts now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.86,
    "endTime": 50.693,
    "text": "Let's go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.693,
    "endTime": 51.53,
    "text": "- You got to run."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.69,
    "endTime": 55.373,
    "text": "There's this toy called Treasure X."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.74,
    "endTime": 58.333,
    "text": "It comes with this little skeleton guy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.63,
    "endTime": 60.74,
    "text": "- [Host] You have to be able to spend it all in an hour."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.74,
    "endTime": 61.623000000000005,
    "text": "- All of it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.63,
    "endTime": 62.463,
    "text": "- All of it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.71,
    "endTime": 64.803,
    "text": "- I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.81,
    "endTime": 66.57000000000001,
    "text": "- [Host] I see an ice cream truck guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.57,
    "endTime": 68.68299999999999,
    "text": "- [Sal] Let's get it before it goes away."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.76,
    "endTime": 70.35000000000001,
    "text": "- [Annie] Finally, we made it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.35,
    "endTime": 71.35,
    "text": "- [Host] We made it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.106,
    "endTime": 74.606,
    "text": "- [Annie] Vanilla."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.35,
    "endTime": 77.18299999999999,
    "text": "- [Host] Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.183,
    "endTime": 78.16000000000001,
    "text": "- One hundred."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.87,
    "endTime": 82.16300000000001,
    "text": "- Here, put it in here and then hold on to it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.44,
    "endTime": 86.14,
    "text": "- We'll go to the toy store first."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.7,
    "endTime": 88.152,
    "text": "Oh be careful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.72,
    "endTime": 102.6,
    "text": "- [Sal] Can I just eat my ice cream now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.6,
    "endTime": 104.44999999999999,
    "text": "- [Host] Yeah, but just so you know time is ticking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.45,
    "endTime": 106.21000000000001,
    "text": "You're gonna have 40 minutes left to spend the money."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.21,
    "endTime": 107.58,
    "text": "You only spent four of the dollars."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.58,
    "endTime": 108.98,
    "text": "What are you gonna get Owen?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.64,
    "endTime": 111.27,
    "text": "- I'm looking for it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.78,
    "endTime": 112.94,
    "text": "That's Minecraft."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.94,
    "endTime": 113.773,
    "text": "- [Host] You like that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.773,
    "endTime": 114.91,
    "text": "- That's a little TNT mug."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.91,
    "endTime": 118.503,
    "text": "Look at it, it's a hilarious mug."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.748,
    "endTime": 119.91000000000001,
    "text": "$9.99."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.91,
    "endTime": 121.253,
    "text": "- [Host] What are you looking for again?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.253,
    "endTime": 125.803,
    "text": "- It's like a piece of gold and a weird skeleton figure."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.34,
    "endTime": 128.70000000000002,
    "text": "I have no idea if it's even here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.699,
    "endTime": 130.949,
    "text": "- Let's see, is there anything else you want?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.15,
    "endTime": 131.983,
    "text": "- Not really."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.56,
    "endTime": 134.8,
    "text": "- If I were a kid I'd be grabbing everything I see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.8,
    "endTime": 136.203,
    "text": "Owen's very particular."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.35,
    "endTime": 137.799,
    "text": "He really wants this one toy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.22,
    "endTime": 140.433,
    "text": "- How many minutes was it already?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.6,
    "endTime": 142.683,
    "text": "At least I got some change back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.6,
    "endTime": 144.46,
    "text": "- There's Dylan's Candy Bar."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.779,
    "endTime": 146.946,
    "text": "- [Skyla] Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.82,
    "endTime": 149.519,
    "text": "- [Host] Anything seem good, that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.87,
    "endTime": 151.833,
    "text": "You gonna get stuff here, what do you like?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.46,
    "endTime": 157.383,
    "text": "You're getting a lot of different stuff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.64,
    "endTime": 161.73899999999998,
    "text": "- Come on Sal, don't be scared of a brain freeze,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.74,
    "endTime": 163.28,
    "text": "you gonna eat so fast right,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.28,
    "endTime": 165.229,
    "text": "'cause we gotta get to spend that money."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.229,
    "endTime": 166.62,
    "text": "(giggling)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.62,
    "endTime": 168.4,
    "text": "What are you going to do with your money now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.4,
    "endTime": 170.4,
    "text": "- [Sal] I'm going to put it in the bank."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.21,
    "endTime": 171.35,
    "text": "- That's, you don't want to get toys,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.35,
    "endTime": 172.63,
    "text": "you want to put it in the bank?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.63,
    "endTime": 174.403,
    "text": "- [Sal] Let's do this money thing!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.56,
    "endTime": 175.883,
    "text": "Are those pigeons?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.91,
    "endTime": 177.76,
    "text": "- Yeah, there are a bunch of pigeons."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.14,
    "endTime": 179.69,
    "text": "- [Annie] There's a lot of pigeons."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.69,
    "endTime": 181.54,
    "text": "- [Host] Come on, don't get distracted."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.54,
    "endTime": 182.373,
    "text": "All right, so we're going to walk"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.373,
    "endTime": 183.57,
    "text": "through the farmer's market."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.57,
    "endTime": 184.82899999999998,
    "text": "- [Sal] I'm getting corn."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.83,
    "endTime": 186.543,
    "text": "- It says five for two dollars."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.12,
    "endTime": 190.703,
    "text": "- It's because I don't want to eat too much corn."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.86,
    "endTime": 195.3,
    "text": "- [Host] Yeah, do you have a plan?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.3,
    "endTime": 197.203,
    "text": "- I don't know, maybe flowers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.59,
    "endTime": 198.51,
    "text": "- These ones."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.51,
    "endTime": 199.85899999999998,
    "text": "- [Host] You want this one?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.77,
    "endTime": 201.27,
    "text": "- Come on spend this money."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.27,
    "endTime": 202.583,
    "text": "I'm buying it for someone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.93,
    "endTime": 204.70000000000002,
    "text": "- Oh, you're buying it for someone?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.7,
    "endTime": 204.903,
    "text": "- Yep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.903,
    "endTime": 205.736,
    "text": "- That's nice of you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.41,
    "endTime": 207.243,
    "text": "It's for me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.302,
    "endTime": 210.873,
    "text": "Oh my god that's so sweet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.56,
    "endTime": 212.91,
    "text": "- [Sal] Is it four dollars?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.874,
    "endTime": 216.707,
    "text": "- Two."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.84,
    "endTime": 218.943,
    "text": "- [Sal] We're really spending this money."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.56,
    "endTime": 230.86,
    "text": "- You're gonna have to pay for the cab though."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.86,
    "endTime": 231.763,
    "text": "- [Owen] Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.17,
    "endTime": 234.23,
    "text": "- You're willing to do it to get to that toy?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.23,
    "endTime": 235.63,
    "text": "- [Owen] Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.648,
    "endTime": 237.10999999999999,
    "text": "- [Host] All right, let's do it, let's hail a cab."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.11,
    "endTime": 237.84400000000002,
    "text": "- Cab!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.793,
    "endTime": 239.626,
    "text": "Hi!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.626,
    "endTime": 241.873,
    "text": "- [Host] How much do you think you're gonna spend at Target?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.54,
    "endTime": 245.89,
    "text": "You know what I think we should see"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.89,
    "endTime": 247.369,
    "text": "how much all this stuff is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.67,
    "endTime": 249.82,
    "text": "to make sure you can get it all, all right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.7,
    "endTime": 254.44199999999998,
    "text": "- Whatever candy I like I got and some random stuff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.93,
    "endTime": 256.743,
    "text": "I want cotton candy please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.959,
    "endTime": 258.5,
    "text": "- [Host] You know how cotton candy gets made?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.5,
    "endTime": 259.333,
    "text": "- With sugar."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.56,
    "endTime": 261.459,
    "text": "My brothers, they're gonna be jealous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.473,
    "endTime": 263.723,
    "text": "(laughing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.813,
    "endTime": 264.646,
    "text": "- Here you go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.713,
    "endTime": 265.713,
    "text": "- Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.51,
    "endTime": 268.693,
    "text": "- I'm going to be the coolest kid in school."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.26,
    "endTime": 271.763,
    "text": "- This is kind of like the craziest contest."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.68,
    "endTime": 275.323,
    "text": "I'm going to pay you by dollars."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.46,
    "endTime": 277.472,
    "text": "How much money is it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.633,
    "endTime": 278.863,
    "text": "- [Cab Driver] $9.90."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.863,
    "endTime": 280.343,
    "text": "- Nine, 10."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.72,
    "endTime": 285.73,
    "text": "Here I'll give you four or five dollars for it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.9,
    "endTime": 285.923,
    "text": "- [Host] Yeah, save some."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.923,
    "endTime": 288.53000000000003,
    "text": "- All right I'll give you a little more."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.31,
    "endTime": 290.833,
    "text": "I know it sounds really expensive but."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.3,
    "endTime": 292.803,
    "text": "I gave a lot of money away."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.49,
    "endTime": 297.32,
    "text": "- [Host] That's why you put it in the bank, to save it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.32,
    "endTime": 300.93,
    "text": "- Because I really don't want to spend that money."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.11,
    "endTime": 301.779,
    "text": "- [Host] Wait a second, Sal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.779,
    "endTime": 302.612,
    "text": "- What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.612,
    "endTime": 304.14000000000004,
    "text": "- Here's a bank, do you want to stop in?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.14,
    "endTime": 305.81,
    "text": "Did you want to stop and put your money in now?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 305.81,
    "endTime": 308.823,
    "text": "- [Sal] No, I want to go to the toy store instead."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.823,
    "endTime": 309.656,
    "text": "- Okay we're going to the toy store."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.656,
    "endTime": 310.48900000000003,
    "text": "Tiles."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.489,
    "endTime": 312.323,
    "text": "- [Host] Do you guys want to buy any tiles?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.739,
    "endTime": 314.179,
    "text": "- [Sal] No. - [Annie] No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.179,
    "endTime": 315.11999999999995,
    "text": "- [Host] No, okay sure."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.211,
    "endTime": 319.51,
    "text": "- [Sal] We're almost there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.51,
    "endTime": 320.217,
    "text": "- [Host] Whew."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320.668,
    "endTime": 322.1,
    "text": "- I'm all right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.18,
    "endTime": 323.13,
    "text": "- [Host] Whew."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 323.955,
    "endTime": 324.928,
    "text": "Do you see it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324.928,
    "endTime": 325.761,
    "text": "- Yeah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 326.27,
    "endTime": 327.883,
    "text": "X marks the spot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.4,
    "endTime": 330.522,
    "text": "- [Host] Do you want to pick out some more stuff to get?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.11,
    "endTime": 335.707,
    "text": "- I might spend the rest on that one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.176,
    "endTime": 338.31,
    "text": "To upstairs!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.31,
    "endTime": 338.864,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.29,
    "endTime": 341.445,
    "text": "- [Host] Careful."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 341.845,
    "endTime": 344.317,
    "text": "- [Owen] Nice, let's take the elevator."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344.317,
    "endTime": 345.333,
    "text": "- [Host] Okay, what do you guys want?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.69,
    "endTime": 348.523,
    "text": "Unicorns?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348.523,
    "endTime": 349.36,
    "text": "What do you like?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.817,
    "endTime": 350.65000000000003,
    "text": "You like unicorns?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 350.65,
    "endTime": 351.483,
    "text": "Should I grab one?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 351.55,
    "endTime": 353.63,
    "text": "Oh okay you want that one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 353.165,
    "endTime": 353.99800000000005,
    "text": "- [Annie] Mm-hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 353.998,
    "endTime": 354.831,
    "text": "- All right good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 354.831,
    "endTime": 355.8,
    "text": "All right, there's one thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.91,
    "endTime": 357.66,
    "text": "That's 10 bucks so you got a lot more you can get."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.66,
    "endTime": 358.49300000000005,
    "text": "- I can hold that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 358.493,
    "endTime": 360.34,
    "text": "- You only have a certain amount of time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 360.34,
    "endTime": 361.173,
    "text": "- [Sal] Found it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 361.173,
    "endTime": 362.503,
    "text": "- [Host] Found, that's something you want?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.503,
    "endTime": 363.883,
    "text": "- Ours is broken now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.5,
    "endTime": 365.41,
    "text": "- [Host] That's smart, that's smart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 365.41,
    "endTime": 366.593,
    "text": "Replace broken things."
  },
